{"tid":2512392,"cid":33,"subCid":0,"title":"西環均益二期法團換屆   開明派六人名單全數當選","createTime":"2021-05-01T16:22:38.000Z","updateTime":"2021-05-02T00:56:26.000Z","uid":51583,"like":13,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"992500c9f1de170edfc3826e2bc07cf3b10efaf9","tid":2512392,"uid":51583,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-05-01T16:22:38.000Z","msg":"位於中聯辦附近的西環均益大廈二期，今（1 日）晚舉行法團換屆選舉。現屆開明派法團 3 年前「踢走」連任逾二十年的親建制法團，惟親建制派今屆組十一人名單捲土重來。<br />\n晚上 10 時許，選法團程序甫開始即爆衝突，參選的建制派一方不滿，開明派臨時欲把 6 人名單籌組為 11 人名單，雙方起閧，口角不斷。<br />\n點票程序最終在混亂中展開，晚上近 12 時，開明派六人名單高票當選，居民歡呼慶祝。由於今屆業主立案法團委員人數議決為 11 人，餘下五席為親建制派。"},{"pid":"30c3b81873c6aac55277c47774c4e7489f583da2","tid":2512392,"uid":125168,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-05-01T16:29:08.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/devil.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0e82e34b42fb4ac69cfc962e2c9c9ece532befde","tid":2512392,"uid":72929,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-05-01T16:30:36.000Z","msg":"出術咪又係輸"},{"pid":"c6e3e57543f2fec0c6533235c43267dc90336d68","tid":2512392,"uid":60831,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-05-01T16:44:27.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0ed774997d89235f5837d6374a668c75e94f0a34","tid":2512392,"uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-05-02T00:56:26.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br